text: How in THE FUCK did George Floyd's death result in protests in London, Toronto and in Berlin all of a sudden?! Seriously?!?

Didn’t know about this #BlackLivesMatter protest but was grateful that it rolled by a couple minutes before I started teaching today. They seemed surprised that I could shout so loud. Thanks, y’all. #BreonnaTaylor #AhmaudArbery #GeorgeFloyd
